---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About - Fabien Salles" 
  description="Discover my journey and vision of software craftsmanship"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">My Vision of Software Craftsmanship</h2>
        <p>
          As a software craftsmanship expert, I am passionate about creating quality software
          that brings real value to users. I firmly believe that software development is an art
          that requires not only technical skills but also a thoughtful approach and rigorous practices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">My Approach</h2>
        <p>
          I focus on several key aspects in my work:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-4">
          <li>
            <strong>Clean Code</strong> - I believe in the importance of clean, readable, and
            maintainable code. Well-written code is an investment for the future.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Testing</strong> - Automated tests are essential for ensuring code quality
            and reliability. I practice and teach TDD (Test-Driven Development).
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Architecture</strong> - Good architecture is key to scalable and maintainable
            software. I favor SOLID principles and hexagonal architecture.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Training</strong> - I share my knowledge through training and technical
            coaching to help teams progress.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Services</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Training</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li>Clean Code and best practices</li>
              <li>Test-Driven Development (TDD)</li>
              <li>Domain-Driven Design (DDD)</li>
              <li>Advanced Git</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Support</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li>Technical coaching</li>
              <li>Code review</li>
              <li>Quality process implementation</li>
              <li>Software architecture</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Contact Me</h2>
        <p>
          Want to discuss your project or learn more about my services?
          Don't hesitate to contact me:
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex gap-4">
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/fabiensalles/"
            class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a
            href="mailto:contact@fabiensalles.dev"
            class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors"
          >
            Email
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>